---
// Highlights Section - Simplified for CREYPASS
// ------------
// Description: A clean section with construction/remodeling focus

// Components
// - Layout
import Section from '../../ui/Section.astro'
import Row from '../../ui/Row.astro'
import Col from '../../ui/Col.astro'
---

<Section padding="both" classes="bg-neutral-50 dark:bg-neutral-900">
	<Row>
		<Col span="12" align="center" classes="mb-8">
			<h2 class="text-pretty text-2xl lg:text-3xl mb-4">¿Por qué elegir <strong>CREYPASS</strong>?</h2>
		</Col>
	</Row>
	
	<!-- Primera fila: Diseño Personalizado -->
	<Row classes="mb-12 lg:mb-16 items-center">
		<Col span="6" classes="pr-4 lg:pr-8">
			<div>
				<h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-primary-600"><strong>Diseño</strong> Personalizado</h3>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
					Creamos espacios únicos que reflejan tu estilo. Desde cocinas modernas hasta baños de lujo, cada detalle pensado para ti.
				</p>
			</div>
		</Col>
		<Col span="6" classes="pl-4 lg:pl-8">
			<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-100 to-primary-200 dark:from-primary-900 dark:to-primary-800 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 h-48 lg:h-64 flex items-center justify-center">
				<div class="text-center">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 lg:w-20 lg:h-20 bg-primary-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 lg:mb-4">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 lg:w-10 lg:h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.387-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<p class="text-primary-700 dark:text-primary-300 font-semibold text-sm lg:text-base">Diseño Arquitectónico</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</Col>
	</Row>

	<!-- Segunda fila: Financiamiento -->
	<Row classes="items-center">
		<Col span="6" classes="pr-4 lg:pr-8">
			<div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-100 to-neutral-200 dark:from-neutral-800 dark:to-neutral-700 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 h-48 lg:h-64 flex items-center justify-center">
				<div class="text-center">
					<div class="w-16 h-16 lg:w-20 lg:h-20 bg-neutral-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 lg:mb-4">
						<svg class="w-8 h-8 lg:w-10 lg:h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
						</svg>
					</div>
					<p class="text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300 font-semibold text-sm lg:text-base">
						<span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold block">7.9%</span>
						<span class="text-xs lg:text-sm">Tasa Fija Anual</span>
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</Col>
		<Col span="6" classes="pl-4 lg:pl-8">
			<div>
				<h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300"><strong>Financiamiento</strong> Sin Complicaciones</h3>
				<p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-300 text-base lg:text-lg leading-relaxed">
					Tasa fija 7.9% anual, sin bancos intermediarios. Transforma tu espacio hoy y paga cómodamente hasta 60 meses.
				</p>
			</div>
		</Col>
	</Row>
</Section>
